channel.title: Breaking news from Animal Planet News Center!
channel.description:
A new species was discovered in the Outback of Australia. This species of Kangaroo is extremely rare and resides in NSW. Only one of these creatures is known to exist, and is believed to have two forms. Half Kangaroo, half human. Scientists have learned that this species has a inner-brit. Scientists will release more as information in received.
[url=http://youtube.com/watch?v=eBGIQ7ZuuiU]Full story[/url] Pictures: [IMG]http://i30.tinypic.com/vgh9tv.jpg[/img]
